Invocation Name: magicians trivia
des: Are you a Magicians superfan? Enroll at Brakebills University and prove yourself worthy of the title “Magician”. Embark on an epic quest and test your Magicians knowledge. Your journey begins with Dean Fogg, who will administer your Brakebills entrance exam. Answer his questions correctly and you’ll move on to train with more of the cast of The Magicians. Beware! If you fail, you’ll go down the path of dark, rebel magicians: The Hedges.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
